TASK 3:
Create standard access-list to allow telnet via gi1 management port to avoid telnet the gi2 and gi3

@int gi 1
conf t
ip access-list standard INT-Gi1
 permit 192.168.182.0 0.0.0.255
exit
!
! apply on the interface
!
line vty 0 14
 access-class INT-Gi1 in
exit
!
ip http access-class ipv4 INT-Gi1

```````````
ACL-LAB(config)#ip http access-class ?      
  <1-99>  Access list number
  ipv4    Restrict http server access by ipv4 access-class
  ipv6    Restrict http server access by ipv6 access-class

ACL-LAB(config)#ip http access-class ipv4 ?
  <1-99>  IPV4 Access list number
  WORD    IPv4 Access list name
